 </a>
 will be giving the 2018-19 Frederick Seitz Lecture on MONDAY, NOVEMBER 5TH, 1:30 PM in KCDB 1103.
</b>
<br/>
Dr. Barkai is Professor at the Weizmann Institute of Science where she is using theoretical and computational tools to investigate system-level properties of biological networks.
